# Git Command Restrictions in Agent Mode

When in agent mode, DO NOT execute any git commands including but not limited to:
- git commit
- git push
- git rebase
- git merge
- git reset --hard
- git checkout -f
- git clean -fd
- Any other destructive git operations

Instead, suggest the commands to the user or provide instructions for manual execution.

Allowed: git status, git log, git diff (read-only operations)